---
title: Quick Sticky Char Siu Chicken & Veggie Stir-Fry with Rapid Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: It’s the beloved char siu pork, also known as Chinese BBQ pork, typically prepared in a sweet BBQ sauce and this one
is pretty close to just that. The sauce is deliciously fragrant and rich perfect, for pork and some stir-fried veggies on a
bed of fluffy rice. If you’re in the mood for a bit of crunch, sprinkle over crispy shallots.
